author: juergen
msg: If the child stores (e.g. contentStore) was not specified in domain.xml, the setParameters method was never called. Now it is called with the store parameters.

msg: the memory store, which inherits from the fileContentStore now inherits the method calls setParameters and initialise to the FileContentStore

author: juergen
msg: if a store (at propFind) throws a NPE the response code is changed to InternalServerErrror and the server prints a stackTrace.
